to crawl through and escape.

157
00:08:06,577 --> 00:08:09,110
They had planned for horizontal drilling. 

158
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:11,547
Using an auger machine.

159
00:08:11,547 --> 00:08:13,228
This is how the machine looks.

160
00:08:13,228 --> 00:08:15,269
Since the first pipe had been passed on the first day,

161
00:08:15,269 --> 00:08:17,777
