encouragement from the people outside.

163
00:08:28,788 --> 00:08:31,589
THDC operated from the other side of the tunnel,

164
00:08:31,589 --> 00:08:34,381
using micro-tunneling techniques.

165
00:08:34,381 --> 00:08:39,828
Additionally, SJVN and ONGC were 
gearing up for vertical drilling if necessary.

166
00:08:39,828 --> 00:08:44,679
Vertical drilling meant drilling a passage 
from the top of the mountain to the tunnel.

167
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:49,131
However, geologists expressed reservations about vertical drilling

168
00:08:49,131 --> 00:08:53,138
due to potential complications with weak stones,

169
00:08:53,138 --> 00:08:57,068
which could lead to further issues or even a landslide.

170
00:08:57,068 --> 00:08:59,075
If it wasn't executed perfectly.

171
00:08:59,075 --> 00:09:01,405
On 14th November, horizontal drilling commenced,

172
