in addition to horizontal openings 

231
00:11:49,738 --> 00:11:50,966
for the rescue operation."

232
00:11:50,966 --> 00:11:53,156
The plan with respect to vertical drilling involved

233
00:11:53,156 --> 00:11:57,217
digging a passage for 90 to 105 meters.

234
00:11:57,217 --> 00:12:00,873
Here, the BRO played a crucial role 
in constructing temporary roads

235
00:12:00,873 --> 00:12:03,761
so that the drilling machines 
could be transported to the top.

236
00:12:03,761 --> 00:12:05,710
This was being done simultaneously,

237
00:12:05,710 --> 00:12:07,760
preparations for vertical drilling began

238
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:10,438
along with the ongoing horizontal drilling from below.

239
00:12:10,438 --> 00:12:13,255
